---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: false
description: "SYNTHERION is a synthwave bullet-hell shooter where every weapon is a loop and every run is a song. Built in Godot."
---

{% include "partials/hero.njk" %}

<main>

<section id="pitch" class="section section--pitch">
  <p class="features__note">You're catching this early. All of the game features below are still taking shape. <a href="{{ site.social.discordInvite }}" rel="noopener">Join the community</a> and help shape what comes next.</p>
  <ul class="features">
    <li>
      <h3>Rhythmic Destruction</h3>
      <p>Nail the beat to earn music-synced weapons.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>A Galaxy in 2D</h3>
      <p>The reach of a space sim, in neon pixels.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Co-op Play</h3>
      <p>Jam sessions from the couch or online.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Beyond Arcade Mode</h3>
      <p>Explore a musical cosmos. Collect and level-up ships.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <aside class="artist-call">
    <h3 class="artist-call__title">Synthwave artists:</h3>
    <p class="artist-call__body">
      Get a corner of the galaxy built from your music.
    </p>
    <a class="btn--discord artist-call__btn" href="/for-musicians/">Learn more →</a>
  </aside>
</section>

{% include "partials/trailer.njk" %}

{% if collections.posts | length %}
<section class="section section--latest">
  <h2 class="section__heading">Latest Transmissions</h2>
  <div class="post-grid post-grid--latest">
    {% for post in collections.posts | limit(3) %}
      {% set post = post %}
      <div class="post-grid__item">
        {% include "partials/post-card.njk" %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="section__more">
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/devlog/">→ All transmissions</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

</main>
